title: Mint club video tutorials were made for new users
body:
Many new users of mint club find it difficult for how to use mint club website and perform operations so I have made some video tutorials on some operations with detailed procedure in order to help the users and to promote mint club some of them are
How to buy Mint tokens from pancake swap 
https://youtu.be/mhzSIFfwGWs
How to create smart tokens on mint club without any coding
https://youtu.be/ZYrvlFJi31Q
Widget link creation and use cases of the widget link
https://youtu.be/4Qb_DR6WEOI
Explained how to purchase Mint Smart tokens in detailed manner
https://youtu.be/b9hgmYev6Kw
Detailed explanation on how to participate in the token objective programs like debate monkey token 
https://youtu.be/mg5bQXpZaNM
Even tough covering all topics is difficult  essential ones are covered and tutorials for remaining topics like bonding curve and all will be covered in the channel soon
